data.description: Discover the charm of this adorable, updated 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home showcasing a delightful open floor plan on the main level, perfect for modern living. Enjoy the convenience of an off-street 2-car garage and revel in the privacy of a fenced-in property encompassing all sides, creating a vast grassy area ideal for outdoor activities and relaxation. This inviting residence offers a harmonious blend of functionality and style, with recent updates enhancing its appeal. Embrace the comfort and warmth of this welcoming abode that seamlessly combines practicality with a touch of character, inviting you to call it your own sweet haven. Don't miss the chance to make cherished memories in this beautifully updated home that offers both convenience and charm! VACANT AND EASY TO SHOW!
